#: ../../docstring maxframe.tensor.c_:1 of
msgid "Translates slice objects to concatenation along the second axis."
msgstr "将切片对象转换为沿第二轴的拼接。"

#: ../../docstring maxframe.tensor.c_:3 of
msgid ""
"This is short-hand for ``mt.r_['-1,2,0', index expression]``, which is "
"useful because of its common occurrence. In particular, tensors will be "
"stacked along their last axis after being upgraded to at least 2-D with "
"1's post-pended to the shape (column vectors made out of 1-D tensors)."
msgstr ""
"这是 ``mt.r_['-1,2,0', 索引表达式]`` 的简写形式，由于其常见用途而非常实用"
"。特别地，张量在被提升为至少二维并在形状后追加1（将一维张量转换为列向量）"
"之后，会沿其最后一个轴进行堆叠。"

#: ../../docstring maxframe.tensor.c_:10 of
msgid ":py:obj:`column_stack`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docstring maxframe.tensor.c_:11 of
msgid "Stack 1-D tensors as columns into a 2-D tensor."
msgstr "将一维张量作为列堆叠成二维张量。"

